	dprr:hasNoteText "Leg., lieut. under M. Antonius (Creticus) in 74. See Syme, Historia 13, 1964, 119-RP 2. 597-598; Wiseman, NM 239-240, no. 245, both with examples of the occurrence of the word as a gentilicium, but agreement that it could be simply a praenomen.[134]\n" ;
	dprr:hasID 7551 .
